title: It's Still Going To Happen | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: It's Still Going To Happen | Joel Osteen
description:
Nothing can stop what God has purposed for your life. What He promised is still going to pass. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
